Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Bloomington, 494 Corridor - South Loop District. Direct access to I-494 and MN-77. Adjacent to the Minneapolis/ St. Paul International Airport and the Mall of America.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: SoLo 3311 features a unique scenic setting at its location situated next to the Minnesota River with views of Minnesota Valley National Wildlife Refuge's wooded buffs, welcoming meadows and peaceful marshlands.The building has an outdoor patio overlooking the river!
